---
<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-claw-500/5 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none" />
  <div class="absolute top-20 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-claw-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none" />
  
  <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-claw-500/10 border border-claw-500/20 text-claw-400 text-sm font-medium mb-8">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-claw-400 animate-pulse" />
        Open Source &middot; Free Forever &middot; Updated May 2026
      </div>
      
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-6">
        The Agentic AI<br />
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-claw-400 to-claw-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Handbook</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl">
        Your AI agent is a chatbot.<br />
        <strong class="bg-gradient-to-r from-claw-400 to-claw-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">It should be a digital employee.</strong>
      </p>

      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-dark-400 leading-relaxed mb-4 max-w-2xl">
        One Austrian developer pushed three text files to GitHub.
        Weeks later Jensen Huang called it
        <em>"the operating system for personal AI."</em>
      </p>

      <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-dark-400 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-2xl">
        This handbook is the operational guide to what comes next:
        autonomous agents that run your business, improve themselves,
        and hand you back your time — built on <strong class="text-white">OpenClaw</strong>, proven in <strong class="text-white">production</strong>.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="#chapters" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-claw-500 hover:bg-claw-600 text-white font-semibold transition-colors">
          Start Reading
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/magnusfroste" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-dark-800 hover:bg-dark-700 text-white font-semibold transition-colors border border-dark-700">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/></svg>
          Clawable on GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-dark-900/50 border border-dark-800/50">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1">20+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-dark-400">Deep-dive chapters</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-dark-900/50 border border-dark-800/50">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1">10</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-dark-400">Laws of agentic architecture</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-dark-900/50 border border-dark-800/50">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1">ADD</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-dark-400">Agent-Driven Development</div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 rounded-xl bg-dark-900/50 border border-dark-800/50">
        <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1">100%</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-dark-400">Open-source &amp; free forever</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
